        "ColbunServiceCountry": "Colbún Service Country and the Municipality of Colbún share their transformative experiences in the various localities of the commune. Dive into their stories, from the revitalization of public spaces to social inclusion projects that have improved the quality of life of neighbors. From educational workshops in rural areas to the promotion of local entrepreneurship, discover how working together has made a difference in the heart of Colbún.",
