        "ColbunBeauty": "In Colbún you can find different attractions that are an entry point to what the rest of the commune has to offer. From the spa and Machicura reservoir to know the characteristic flora and fauna, as well as old buildings that were a fundamental part of the productivity of the area as the old mill and the commemorative square of the small train, a historic means of transport in the area. Colbún is constituted as a center with different services where you can enjoy and stock up to know our beautiful commune.",
