        "GuardiaRemember": "La Guardia is a perfect place to disconnect from the world. In the middle of a natural landscape, close to Lake Colbún, in the middle of trees, it is a place to rest, to walk around and to create memories with the typical activities that take place in the area. La Guardia still preserves traditions that pass from generation to generation and that are important to know and maintain.",
